      <title>德国商业银行改组财富管理部门，扩大超级富豪业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/commerzbank-revamps-wealth-unit-to-grow-business-with-ultra-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 正在加大力度为超级富豪提供财富管理服务，以增加费用收入并抵御竞争对手意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 的主动接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/commerzbank-revamps-wealth-unit-to-grow-business-with-ultra-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
